    <title type="text">Debugging SAPscripts in SAP</title>
    <id>urn:uuid:472e4dcf-de49-36cf-9beb-54daa7fd5141</id>
    <updated>2019-10-06T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <link href="https://jeevanCd.github.io/blog/debugging-sapscripts-in-sap/" />
    <author>
      <name>Jeevan Chand</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;To activate SAP Script debugger:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Step 1:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Go to Transaction SE38.
Enter the program name RSTXDBUG
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/blog/debugging-sapscripts-in-sap/snap1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;snap1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Press Execute.
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/blog/debugging-sapscripts-in-sap/script1.gif&quot; alt=&quot;script1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Step 2:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Go to SE71.

In the initial screen, Enter the form name and click on Utilities --&amp;gt; Activate Debugger
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/blog/debugging-sapscripts-in-sap/script2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;script2&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/blog/debugging-sapscripts-in-sap/script1.gif&quot; alt=&quot;script1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
